📌 Project Overview

Awais Fitness Coaching is designed to help beginners and fitness enthusiasts by offering:

Fitness education (bulking, cutting, muscle gain)

Budget-friendly diet plans

Calorie requirement calculator

Structured workout routines

Health monitoring (heart rate, hydration, sleep, steps)

Injury prevention tips

Beginner fitness FAQs

Inclusive workouts for disabled users

The project originally started as a console-based application and was later converted into a GUI-based desktop app for better usability and user experience.

🖥️ GUI Features

🎯 User-friendly interface (Tkinter)

🧠 Fitness terms & education

🥗 Weight gain / loss / muscle gain diet plans

🔢 Daily calorie calculator

🏋️‍♂️ Full workout plans (6-day split)

🫀 Heartbeat & health status evaluation

💧 Hydration & sleep analysis

🤕 Injury prevention tips

❓ 100+ beginner fitness FAQs

♿ Special workout plans for disabled users

📊 Scrollable output panel for clean display

🛠️ Technologies Used

Python 3

Tkinter (GUI framework)

Standard Python libraries only (no external dependencies)

