▶️ How to Run the Project
1️⃣ Clone the Repository
git clone https://github.com/your-username/awais-fitness-coaching.git

2️⃣ Navigate to the Project Folder
cd awais-fitness-coaching

3️⃣ Run the Application
python awais_fitness_gui.py


✅ Make sure Python 3 is installed on your system.

🧮 Calorie Calculation Formula

The app uses the Mifflin-St Jeor Equation:

Calories = 10 × weight(kg) + 6.25 × height(cm) − 5 × age − 161


This estimates minimum daily calorie needs.

